    "description": "LG Soft India Holdings Services, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Senior Software Engineer for our Tiruchirappalli operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout LG Soft India Holdings Services:\nLG Soft India Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with LG Soft India Holdings Services!",
